---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Newsletter — The Narrow March" description="Daily exegesis from the week's sermon. Every week, one passage. Every day, we go deeper.">

  <!-- Page Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero-bg">
      <img src="/images/banner-alt.jpg" alt="" />
    </div>
    <div class="page-hero-content">
      <p class="page-hero-label">Daily Exegesis</p>
      <h1>The Narrow March Newsletter</h1>
      <p class="page-hero-subtitle">Every week, one passage. Every day, we go deeper.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Intro -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="intro-block">
        <div class="decorative-line decorative-line-center"></div>
        <p class="intro-text">
          Most men hear a sermon and forget it by lunch. The Narrow March won't let you. Each week we take one passage and live in it —
          daily exegesis that breaks the text open so deep that by Sunday, the Word preaches itself.
          Scripture wasn't meant to be skimmed. Neither is this.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Works -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title" style="text-align:center;">How It Works</h2>
      <div class="decorative-line decorative-line-center"></div>
      <div class="how-grid">
        <div class="how-step">
          <div class="step-number">01</div>
          <div class="step-content card">
            <h3>One Passage Per Week</h3>
            <p>Tied to the weekly sermon. We don't hop around — we dig in and stay until the text has done its work.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="how-step">
          <div class="step-number">02</div>
          <div class="step-content card">
            <h3>Daily Delivery</h3>
            <p>Each day unpacks a different layer — context, language, theology, application. By Sunday, you own it.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="how-step">
          <div class="step-number">03</div>
          <div class="step-content card">
            <h3>Verse by Verse</h3>
            <p>No surface-level summaries. We break the text down word by word, because the details are where the power lives.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Banner -->
  <section class="cta-banner">
    <div class="cta-banner-bg">
      <img src="/images/hero-banner.jpg" alt="" />
    </div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2>Subscribe to The Narrow March</h2>
        <div class="decorative-line decorative-line-center" style="background:#fff;"></div>
        <p>Daily exegesis from the week's sermon. The Word isn't something you heard once — it's something you carry.</p>
        <a href="https://blog.thenarrowmarch.com" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Subscribe Now</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Cross-link -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="crosslink card">
        <div class="card-accent-top"></div>
        <div class="crosslink-inner">
          <div>
            <h3>Also from The Narrow March</h3>
            <p>
              <strong>The Daily Crusader</strong> — a separate daily devotional at 5 AM,
              drawn from the 365-day book. The Crusader gives you your marching orders. The Newsletter takes you deeper into the text.
              They're built to work together.
            </p>
          </div>
          <a href="/daily-crusader" class="btn btn-outline">Learn More</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .intro-block {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .intro-text {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.9;
  }

  /* ===== How Grid ===== */
  .how-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
  }

  .how-step {
    position: relative;
  }

  .step-number {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--accent);
    opacity: 0.2;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: -0.5rem;
    padding-left: 0.5rem;
  }

  .step-content {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .step-content .card-accent-top {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), var(--gold));
  }

  .step-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .step-content p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  /* ===== CTA Banner ===== */
  .cta-banner {
    position: relative;
    padding: 6rem 0;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .cta-banner-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
  }

  .cta-banner-bg img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .cta-banner-bg::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.82);
  }

  .cta-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .cta-content h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-content p {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* ===== Cross-link ===== */
  .crosslink {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .crosslink-inner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .crosslink h3 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .crosslink p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .crosslink .card-accent-top {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), var(--gold));
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .how-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .crosslink-inner {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>
